            <title>中國極氪研發「金磚電池」   充電 15 分鐘續航 500 公里</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/20/china-zeekr-gold-battery-15-min-500-km/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=china-zeekr-gold-battery-15-min-500-km</link>
